Hi Yall <!here> :wave: - :sprocket: HubSpot is doing a few (free) virtual developer events over the next few months. :tada:
> The next one will be an :robot_face: *API Developer,  Ask Me Anything* :robot_face: on October 26th, 12PM-1PM EST (next week).
> Great place to ask questions about API, integrations, connect program, product vision, etc.
:point_right: You can learn more and save your spot here: <https://developers.HubSpot.com/developer-ama>
